{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I really am honored to be here, and as Chris said,"},{"time":3000,"text":"it's been over 20 years since I started working in Africa."},{"time":6000,"text":"My first introduction was at the Abidjan airport on a sweaty, Ivory Coast morning."},{"time":12000,"text":"I had just left Wall Street, cut my hair to look like Margaret Mead,"},{"time":16000,"text":"given away most everything that I owned,"},{"time":18000,"text":"and arrived with all the essentials --"},{"time":20000,"text":"some poetry, a few clothes, and, of course, a guitar --"},{"time":22000,"text":"because I was going to save the world,"},{"time":24000,"text":"and I thought I would just start with the African continent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"But literally within days of arriving I was told, in no uncertain terms,"},{"time":34000,"text":"by a number of West African women, that Africans didn't want saving,"},{"time":39000,"text":"thank you very much, least of all not by me."},{"time":41000,"text":"I was too young, unmarried, I had no children,"},{"time":44000,"text":"didn't really know Africa, and besides, my French was pitiful."},{"time":48000,"text":"And so, it was an incredibly painful time in my life,"},{"time":51000,"text":"and yet it really started to give me the humility to start listening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56000,"text":"I think that failure can be an incredibly motivating force as well,"},{"time":60000,"text":"so I moved to Kenya and worked in Uganda,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and I met a group of Rwandan women, who asked me, in 1986,"},{"time":66000,"text":"to move to Kigali to help them start the first microfinance institution there."},{"time":70000,"text":"And I did, and we ended up naming it Duterimbere,"},{"time":74000,"text":"meaning \"to go forward with enthusiasm.\" And while we were doing it,"},{"time":77000,"text":"I realized that there weren't a lot of businesses that were viable"},{"time":80000,"text":"and started by women, and so maybe I should try to run a business, too."},{"time":84000,"text":"And so I started looking around, and I heard about a bakery"},{"time":86000,"text":"that was run by 20 prostitutes."},{"time":88000,"text":"And, being a little intrigued, I went to go meet this group,"},{"time":92000,"text":"and what I found was 20 unwed mothers who were trying to survive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97000,"text":"And it was really the beginning of my understanding the power of language,"},{"time":102000,"text":"and how what we call people so often distances us from them,"},{"time":105000,"text":"and makes them little."},{"time":107000,"text":"I also found out that the bakery was nothing like a business,"},{"time":111000,"text":"that, in fact, it was a classic charity run by a well-intentioned person,"},{"time":115000,"text":"who essentially spent 600 dollars a month"},{"time":119000,"text":"to keep these 20 women busy making little crafts and baked goods,"},{"time":124000,"text":"and living on 50 cents a day, still in poverty."},{"time":127000,"text":"So, I made a deal with the women. I said, \"Look, we get rid of the charity side,"},{"time":130000,"text":"and we run this as a business and I'll help you.\""},{"time":133000,"text":"They nervously agreed. I nervously started, and, of course,"},{"time":137000,"text":"things are always harder than you think they're going to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"First of all, I thought, well, we need a sales team,"},{"time":141000,"text":"and we clearly aren't the A-Team here,"},{"time":143000,"text":"so let's -- I did all this training."},{"time":146000,"text":"And the epitome was when I literally marched into the streets"},{"time":150000,"text":"of Nyamirambo, which is the popular quarter of Kigali, with a bucket,"},{"time":153000,"text":"and I sold all these little doughnuts to people,"},{"time":156000,"text":"and I came back, and I was like, \"You see?\""},{"time":158000,"text":"And the women said, \"You know, Jacqueline, who in Nyamirambo is not going to buy"},{"time":162000,"text":"doughnuts out of an orange bucket from a tall American woman?\" And like --"},{"time":166000,"text":"(Laughter) -- it's a good point."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168000,"text":"So then I went the whole American way,"},{"time":170000,"text":"with competitions, team and individual. Completely failed,"},{"time":173000,"text":"but over time, the women learnt to sell on their own way."},{"time":177000,"text":"And they started listening to the marketplace,"},{"time":179000,"text":"and they came back with ideas for cassava chips, and banana chips,"},{"time":182000,"text":"and sorghum bread, and before you knew it,"},{"time":184000,"text":"we had cornered the Kigali market,"},{"time":186000,"text":"and the women were earning three to four times the national average."},{"time":189000,"text":"And with that confidence surge, I thought, \"Well, it's time to create a real bakery,"},{"time":193000,"text":"so let's paint it.\" And the women said, \"That's a really great idea.\""},{"time":197000,"text":"And I said, \"Well, what color do you want to paint it?\" And they said,"},{"time":199000,"text":"\"Well, you choose.\" And I said, \"No, no, I'm learning to listen."},{"time":202000,"text":"You choose. It's your bakery, your street, your country -- not mine.\""},{"time":205000,"text":"But they wouldn't give me an answer."},{"time":207000,"text":"So, one week, two weeks, three weeks went by,"},{"time":209000,"text":"and finally I said, \"Well, how about blue?\""},{"time":212000,"text":"And they said, \"Blue, blue, we love blue. Let's do it blue.\""},{"time":214000,"text":"So, I went to the store, I brought Gaudence, the recalcitrant one of all,"},{"time":218000,"text":"and we brought all this paint and fabric to make curtains,"},{"time":222000,"text":"and on painting day, we all gathered in Nyamirambo,"},{"time":225000,"text":"and the idea was we would paint it white with blue as trim,"},{"time":228000,"text":"like a little French bakery. But that was clearly not as satisfying"},{"time":231000,"text":"as painting a wall of blue like a morning sky."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234000,"text":"So, blue, blue, everything became blue."},{"time":237000,"text":"The walls were blue, the windows were blue,"},{"time":238000,"text":"the sidewalk out front was painted blue."},{"time":241000,"text":"And Aretha Franklin was shouting \"R-E-S-P-E-C-T,\""},{"time":245000,"text":"the women's hips were swaying"},{"time":247000,"text":"and little kids were trying to grab the paintbrushes, but it was their day."},{"time":250000,"text":"And at the end of it, we stood across the street"},{"time":253000,"text":"and we looked at what we had done, and I said, \"It is so beautiful.\""},{"time":256000,"text":"And the women said, \"It really is.\""},{"time":258000,"text":"And I said, \"And I think the color is perfect,\""},{"time":261000,"text":"and they all nodded their head, except for Gaudence,"},{"time":263000,"text":"and I said, \"What?\""},{"time":265000,"text":"And she said, \"Nothing.\" And I said, \"What?\""},{"time":267000,"text":"And she said, \"Well, it is pretty, but, you know, our color, really, it is green.\" And --"},{"time":273000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":276000,"text":"-- I learned then that listening isn't just about patience,"},{"time":281000,"text":"but that when you've lived on charity and dependent your whole life long,"},{"time":286000,"text":"it's really hard to say what you mean."},{"time":288000,"text":"And, mostly because people never really ask you,"},{"time":292000,"text":"and when they do, you don't really think they want to know the truth."},{"time":295000,"text":"And so then I learned that listening is not only about waiting,"},{"time":298000,"text":"but it's also learning how better to ask questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302000,"text":"And so, I lived in Kigali for about two and a half years, doing these two things,"},{"time":306000,"text":"and it was an extraordinary time in my life."},{"time":308000,"text":"And it taught me three lessons"},{"time":310000,"text":"that I think are so important for us today,"},{"time":313000,"text":"and certainly in the work that I do."},{"time":315000,"text":"The first is that dignity is more important to the human spirit than wealth."},{"time":319000,"text":"As Eleni has said, when people gain income, they gain choice,"},{"time":323000,"text":"and that is fundamental to dignity."},{"time":325000,"text":"But as human beings, we also want to see each other,"},{"time":328000,"text":"and we want to be heard by each other, and we should never forget that."},{"time":332000,"text":"The second is that traditional charity and aid"},{"time":335000,"text":"are never going to solve the problems of poverty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337000,"text":"I think Andrew pretty well covered that, so I will move to the third point,"},{"time":340000,"text":"which is that markets alone also"},{"time":342000,"text":"are not going to solve the problems of poverty."},{"time":345000,"text":"Yes, we ran this as a business,"},{"time":347000,"text":"but someone needed to pay the philanthropic support"},{"time":352000,"text":"that came into the training, and the management support, the strategic advice"},{"time":355000,"text":"and, maybe most important of all,"},{"time":358000,"text":"the access to new contacts, networks and new markets."},{"time":362000,"text":"And so, on a micro level, there's a real role for this combination"},{"time":366000,"text":"of investment and philanthropy."},{"time":369000,"text":"And on a macro level -- some of the speakers have inferred that"},{"time":373000,"text":"even health should be privatized."},{"time":375000,"text":"But, having had a father with heart disease,"},{"time":377000,"text":"and realizing that what our family could afford"},{"time":381000,"text":"was not what he should have gotten,"},{"time":384000,"text":"and having a good friend step in to help,"},{"time":387000,"text":"I really believe that all people deserve access to health"},{"time":390000,"text":"at prices they can afford."},{"time":392000,"text":"I think the market can help us figure that out,"},{"time":394000,"text":"but there's got to be a charitable component,"},{"time":396000,"text":"or I don't think we're going to create the kind of societies we want to live in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400000,"text":"And so, it was really those lessons that made me decide to"},{"time":403000,"text":"build Acumen Fund about six years ago."},{"time":406000,"text":"It's a nonprofit, venture capital fund for the poor,"},{"time":409000,"text":"a few oxymorons in one sentence."},{"time":411000,"text":"It essentially raises charitable funds from individuals, foundations and corporations,"},{"time":416000,"text":"and then we turn around and we invest equity and loans"},{"time":418000,"text":"in both for-profit and nonprofit entities"},{"time":420000,"text":"that deliver affordable health, housing, energy, clean water"},{"time":424000,"text":"to low income people in South Asia and Africa,"},{"time":427000,"text":"so that they can make their own choices."},{"time":429000,"text":"We've invested about 20 million dollars in 20 different enterprises,"},{"time":433000,"text":"and have, in so doing, created nearly 20,000 jobs,"},{"time":438000,"text":"and delivered tens of millions of services to people"},{"time":440000,"text":"who otherwise would not be able to afford them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444000,"text":"I want to tell you two stories. Both of them are in Africa."},{"time":447000,"text":"Both of them are about investing in entrepreneurs"},{"time":449000,"text":"who are committed to service, and who really know the markets."},{"time":453000,"text":"Both of them live at the confluence of public health and enterprise,"},{"time":457000,"text":"and both of them, because they're manufacturers,"},{"time":459000,"text":"create jobs directly, and create incomes indirectly,"},{"time":462000,"text":"because they're in the malaria sector,"},{"time":464000,"text":"and Africa loses about 13 billion dollars a year because of malaria."},{"time":469000,"text":"And so as people get healthier, they also get wealthier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":473000,"text":"The first one is called Advanced Bio-Extracts Limited."},{"time":476000,"text":"It's a company built in Kenya about seven years ago"},{"time":478000,"text":"by an incredible entrepreneur named Patrick Henfrey and his three colleagues."},{"time":482000,"text":"These are old-hand farmers"},{"time":484000,"text":"who've gone through all the agricultural ups and downs"},{"time":486000,"text":"in Kenya over the last 30 years."},{"time":488000,"text":"Now, this plant is an Artemisia plant;"},{"time":491000,"text":"it's the basic component for artemisinin,"},{"time":493000,"text":"which is the best-known treatment for malaria."},{"time":495000,"text":"It's indigenous to China and the Far East,"},{"time":499000,"text":"but given that the prevalence of malaria is here in Africa,"},{"time":501000,"text":"Patrick and his colleagues said, \"Let's bring it here,"},{"time":505000,"text":"because it's a high value-add product.\""},{"time":507000,"text":"The farmers get three to four times the yields that they would with maize."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513000,"text":"And so, using patient capital -- money that they could raise early on,"},{"time":517000,"text":"that actually got below market returns"},{"time":519000,"text":"and was willing to go the long haul and be combined"},{"time":523000,"text":"with management assistance, strategic assistance --"},{"time":526000,"text":"they've now created a company where they purchase from 7,500 farmers."},{"time":530000,"text":"So that's about 50,000 people affected."},{"time":532000,"text":"And I think some of you may have visited --"},{"time":534000,"text":"these farmers are helped by KickStart and TechnoServe,"},{"time":537000,"text":"who help them become more self-sufficient."},{"time":539000,"text":"They buy it, they dry it and they bring it to this factory,"},{"time":542000,"text":"which was purchased in part by, again, patient capital from Novartis,"},{"time":546000,"text":"who has a real interest in getting the powder"},{"time":549000,"text":"so that they can make Coartem."},{"time":552000,"text":"Acumen's been working with ABE for the past year, year and a half,"},{"time":557000,"text":"both on looking at a new business plan,"},{"time":559000,"text":"and what does expansion look like, helping with management support"},{"time":562000,"text":"and helping to do term sheets and raise capital."},{"time":566000,"text":"And I really understood what patient capital meant emotionally"},{"time":569000,"text":"in the last month or so. Because the company was literally"},{"time":573000,"text":"10 days away from proving that the product they produced"},{"time":577000,"text":"was at the world-quality level needed to make Coartem,"},{"time":581000,"text":"when they were in the biggest cash crisis of their history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":584000,"text":"And we called all of the social investors we know."},{"time":587000,"text":"Now, some of these same social investors are really interested in Africa"},{"time":591000,"text":"and understand the importance of agriculture,"},{"time":593000,"text":"and they even helped the farmers."},{"time":596000,"text":"And even when we explained that if ABE goes away,"},{"time":599000,"text":"all those 7,500 jobs go away too,"},{"time":603000,"text":"we sometimes have this bifurcation between business and the social."},{"time":608000,"text":"And it's really time we start thinking more creatively about how they can be fused."},{"time":612000,"text":"So Acumen made not one, but two bridge loans,"},{"time":615000,"text":"and the good news is they did indeed meet world-quality classification and are now"},{"time":621000,"text":"in the final stages of closing a 20-million-dollar round, to move it to the next level,"},{"time":625000,"text":"and I think that this will be one of the more important companies in East Africa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":631000,"text":"This is Samuel. He's a farmer."},{"time":633000,"text":"He was actually living in the Kibera slums"},{"time":635000,"text":"when his father called him and told him about Artemisia and the value-add potential."},{"time":640000,"text":"So he moved back to the farm, and, long story short,"},{"time":643000,"text":"they now have seven acres under cultivation."},{"time":646000,"text":"Samuel's kids are in private school,"},{"time":648000,"text":"and he's starting to help other farmers in the area also go into Artemisia production --"},{"time":654000,"text":"dignity being more important than wealth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":657000,"text":"The next one, many of you know."},{"time":660000,"text":"I talked about it a little at Oxford two years ago,"},{"time":663000,"text":"and some of you visited A to Z manufacturing,"},{"time":665000,"text":"which is one of the great, real companies in East Africa."},{"time":669000,"text":"It's another one that lives at the confluence of health and enterprise."},{"time":674000,"text":"And this is really a story about a public-private solution"},{"time":678000,"text":"that has really worked."},{"time":680000,"text":"It started in Japan. Sumitomo had developed a technology"},{"time":684000,"text":"essentially to impregnate a polyethylene-based fiber with organic insecticide,"},{"time":688000,"text":"so you could create a bed net,"},{"time":690000,"text":"a malaria bed net, that would last five years and not need to be re-dipped."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693000,"text":"It could alter the vector, but like Artemisia,"},{"time":696000,"text":"it had been produced only in East Asia. And as part of its social responsibility,"},{"time":700000,"text":"Sumitomo said, \"Why don't we experiment"},{"time":702000,"text":"with whether we can produce it in Africa, for Africans?\""},{"time":705000,"text":"UNICEF came forward and said, \"We'll buy most of the nets,"},{"time":708000,"text":"and then we'll give them away, as part of the global fund's"},{"time":711000,"text":"and the U.N.'s commitment to pregnant women and children, for free.\""},{"time":717000,"text":"Acumen came in with the patient capital,"},{"time":720000,"text":"and we also helped to identify the entrepreneur"},{"time":722000,"text":"that we would all partner with here in Africa,"},{"time":725000,"text":"and Exxon provided the initial resin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":728000,"text":"Well, in looking around for entrepreneurs,"},{"time":730000,"text":"there was none better that we could find on earth than Anuj Shah,"},{"time":733000,"text":"in A to Z manufacturing company."},{"time":735000,"text":"It's a 40-year-old company, it understands manufacturing."},{"time":738000,"text":"It's gone from socialist Tanzania into capitalist Tanzania,"},{"time":741000,"text":"and continued to flourish. It had about 1,000 employees when we first found it."},{"time":746000,"text":"And so, Anuj took the entrepreneurial risk here in Africa"},{"time":749000,"text":"to produce a public good that was purchased by the aid establishment"},{"time":754000,"text":"to work with malaria."}]},{"cues":[{"time":757000,"text":"And, long story short, again, they've been so successful."},{"time":760000,"text":"In our first year, the first net went off the line in October of 2003."},{"time":765000,"text":"We thought the hitting-it-out-of-the-box number was 150,000 nets a year."},{"time":770000,"text":"This year, they are now producing eight million nets a year,"},{"time":773000,"text":"and they employ 5,000 people, 90 percent of whom are women, mostly unskilled."},{"time":778000,"text":"They're in a joint venture with Sumitomo."},{"time":781000,"text":"And so, from an enterprise perspective for Africa,"},{"time":784000,"text":"and from a public health perspective, these are real successes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787000,"text":"But it's only half the story if we're really looking at solving problems of poverty,"},{"time":791000,"text":"because it's not long-term sustainable."},{"time":793000,"text":"It's a company with one big customer."},{"time":795000,"text":"And if avian flu hits, or for any other reason"},{"time":799000,"text":"the world decides that malaria is no longer as much of a priority, everybody loses."},{"time":804000,"text":"And so, Anuj and Acumen"},{"time":807000,"text":"have been talking about testing the private sector,"},{"time":810000,"text":"because the assumption that the aid establishment has made is that,"},{"time":815000,"text":"look, in a country like Tanzania,"},{"time":817000,"text":"80 percent of the population makes less than two dollars a day."},{"time":819000,"text":"It costs, at manufacturing point, six dollars to produce these,"},{"time":823000,"text":"and it costs the establishment another six dollars to distribute it,"},{"time":828000,"text":"so the market price in a free market would be about 12 dollars per net."},{"time":832000,"text":"Most people can't afford that, so let's give it away free."},{"time":834000,"text":"And we said, \"Well, there's another option."},{"time":837000,"text":"Let's use the market as the best listening device we have, and"},{"time":840000,"text":"understand at what price people would pay for this, so they get the dignity of choice."},{"time":845000,"text":"We can start building local distribution,"},{"time":847000,"text":"and actually, it can cost the public sector much less.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":851000,"text":"And so we came in with a second round of patient capital to A to Z,"},{"time":855000,"text":"a loan as well as a grant, so that A to Z could play with pricing"},{"time":859000,"text":"and listen to the marketplace, and found a number of things."},{"time":862000,"text":"One, that people will pay different prices,"},{"time":864000,"text":"but the overwhelming number of people will come forth at one dollar per net"},{"time":868000,"text":"and make a decision to buy it."},{"time":870000,"text":"And when you listen to them, they'll also have a lot to say"},{"time":873000,"text":"about what they like and what they don't like."},{"time":875000,"text":"And that some of the channels we thought would work didn't work."},{"time":879000,"text":"But because of this experimentation and iteration that was allowed"},{"time":882000,"text":"because of the patient capital,"},{"time":884000,"text":"we've now found that it costs about a dollar in the private sector"},{"time":887000,"text":"to distribute, and a dollar to buy the net."},{"time":889000,"text":"So then, from a policy perspective, when you start with the market,"},{"time":893000,"text":"we have a choice."},{"time":894000,"text":"We can continue going along at 12 dollars a net, and the customer pays zero,"},{"time":900000,"text":"or we could at least experiment with some of it, to charge one dollar a net,"},{"time":906000,"text":"costing the public sector another six dollars a net,"},{"time":909000,"text":"give the people the dignity of choice, and have a distribution system"},{"time":913000,"text":"that might, over time, start sustaining itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":916000,"text":"We've got to start having conversations like this,"},{"time":918000,"text":"and I don't think there's any better way to start than using the market,"},{"time":922000,"text":"but also to bring other people to the table around it."},{"time":926000,"text":"Whenever I go to visit A to Z, I think of my grandmother, Stella."},{"time":933000,"text":"She was very much like those women sitting behind the sewing machines."},{"time":938000,"text":"She grew up on a farm in Austria, very poor,"},{"time":940000,"text":"didn't have very much education."},{"time":942000,"text":"She moved to the United States, where she met my grandfather,"},{"time":944000,"text":"who was a cement hauler,"},{"time":946000,"text":"and they had nine children. Three of them died as babies."},{"time":952000,"text":"My grandmother had tuberculosis, and she worked in a sewing machine shop,"},{"time":955000,"text":"making shirts for about 10 cents an hour."},{"time":958000,"text":"She, like so many of the women I see at A to Z,"},{"time":962000,"text":"worked hard every day, understood what suffering was,"},{"time":965000,"text":"had a deep faith in God, loved her children"},{"time":968000,"text":"and would never have accepted a handout."},{"time":971000,"text":"But because she had the opportunity of the marketplace,"},{"time":975000,"text":"and she lived in a society that provided the safety"},{"time":978000,"text":"of having access to affordable health and education,"},{"time":982000,"text":"her children and their children were able to live"},{"time":986000,"text":"lives of real purpose and follow real dreams."}]},{"cues":[{"time":989000,"text":"I look around at my siblings and my cousins -- and as I said,"},{"time":993000,"text":"there are a lot of us --"},{"time":995000,"text":"and I see teachers and musicians, hedge fund managers, designers."},{"time":1001000,"text":"One sister who makes other people's wishes come true."},{"time":1004000,"text":"And my wish, when I see those women, I meet those farmers,"},{"time":1009000,"text":"and I think about all the people across this continent"},{"time":1012000,"text":"who are working hard every day,"},{"time":1014000,"text":"is that they have that sense of opportunity and possibility,"},{"time":1018000,"text":"and that they also can believe and get access to services,"},{"time":1023000,"text":"so that their children, too, can live those lives of great purpose."},{"time":1027000,"text":"It shouldn't be that difficult."},{"time":1029000,"text":"But what it takes is a commitment from all of us"},{"time":1033000,"text":"to essentially refuse trite assumptions,"},{"time":1037000,"text":"get out of our ideological boxes."},{"time":1040000,"text":"It takes investing in those entrepreneurs that are committed"},{"time":1043000,"text":"to service as well as to success."},{"time":1047000,"text":"It takes opening your arms, both, wide,"},{"time":1050000,"text":"and expecting very little love in return,"},{"time":1053000,"text":"but demanding accountability,"},{"time":1055000,"text":"and bringing the accountability to the table as well."},{"time":1058000,"text":"And most of all, most of all,"},{"time":1061000,"text":"it requires that all of us have the courage and the patience,"},{"time":1065000,"text":"whether we are rich or poor, African or non-African,"},{"time":1068000,"text":"local or diaspora, left or right,"},{"time":1071000,"text":"to really start listening to each other."},{"time":1073000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":1075000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}